videos.description: Phil Booth finds Jalen Brunson off the screen and he drains a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Villanova's Brunson getting off to great start

videos.description: Eric Paschall grabs the rebound and throws down a hard slam.
videos.headline: Villanova's Paschall cleans up with jam

videos.description: Mike Smith takes the in-bounds pass and flashes to the basket, finishing with the reverse layup.
videos.headline: Columbia's Smith nifty around the basket

videos.description: Jalen Brunson speeds past his defender and  double pumps for the reverse layup.
videos.headline: Villanova's Brunson finishes with acrobatic layup

videos.description: Omari Spellman finds Mikal; Bridges in the corner and he drives and dunks all over Lukas Meisner.
videos.headline: Villanova's Bridges scores with a vicious dunk
